PFB the steps to run the images:


1. Copy the git project on any linux VM. Go to the assignment directory. 

2. Steps to install docker-compose:

	1. pip install docker-compose


	2. If you get the error :Error: ERROR: client and server don't have same version (client : 1.21, server: 1.18)

	Solution :Run the command below
		  export COMPOSE_API_VERSION=1.18

3. Use the  following command to start the conatiners:

 docker-compose up --build

4. Check the conatiner using command : docker ps

5. Hit the nginx conatiner using IE or using the following command on the same host:

	curl -i localhost:80

